{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"7282deb1-2893-4c9a-8b6f-c20d84d48edf","content":"The template has a solid foundation but is **not quite ready** to publish. Here's what's missing or should be addressed:\n\n**Required/Critical:**\n- `$schema` — add `\"$schema\": \"http://json.schemastore.org/template\"` for validation support.\n- `\"groupIdentity\"` — recommended for NuGet so multiple versions coexist cleanly.\n- `\"preferNameDirectory\": true` — standard for project templates.\n\n**Strongly Recommended:**\n- `\"description\"` — NuGet listing will look incomplete without it.\n- `\"defaultName\"` — fallback project name if user doesn't provide one.\n\n**Nice-to-Have:**\n- `\"precedence\"` — useful if you ship multiple versions in one package.\n\n**Looks Good:**\n- `identity`, `name`, `shortName`, `author`, `classifications`, `tags`, and `symbols` are all well-formed.\n\nIn short: add at minimum a `description` and `$schema`, and consider `groupIdentity` before publishing.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"b401c003-9fed-49f5-99fc-8db7856156b3","outputTokens":241,"requestId":"A785:D40E:164C5B5:18E831A:6A051FCE"},"id":"bc2e6834-911c-429b-8830-a075bb92a9cc","timestamp":"2026-05-14T01:05:26.396Z","parentId":"b4ece5b4-0663-488a-99db-58148641a294"}
